description:
Operators of marinas. Services provided may include boat slip rental,
boat storage, boat cleaning, incidental boat repair, and the retail sale
of marine supplies. This MCC includes merchants located at a marina
that sell gasoline for consumer use in boats, and that do not have a
separate merchant agreement from that of the marina.
For service station merchants located at a marina that have a
separate merchant agreement from that of the marina, use MCC
5541.
